402
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,710
Ili zvati mamu?

403
00:36:03,454 --> 00:36:04,632
Ti jebena curo!

404
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:06,612
Hajde, ti pokvareno derište.

405
